            <li><a href=\"/recruit/work/#person\">こんな人と働きたい</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit/work/#message\">人事部長メッセージ</a></li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <div class=\"l-mega-nav__accord js-accordion-trigger\">\n            <div class=\"c-ttl-primary\"><span class=\"ttl-en\">Career Design</span> <span class=\"ttl-jp\">キャリアデザイン</span></div><button class=\"trigger\" aria-label=\"メニューを開く\"></button>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"l-mega-nav__panel js-accordion-panel\">\n            <div>\n              <ul class=\"l-mega-nav__children\">\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit/education/\">研修・育成</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit/internship/\">インターンシップ</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit/welfare/\">福利厚生</a></li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <div class=\"l-mega-nav__accord js-accordion-trigger\">\n            <div class=\"c-ttl-primary\"><span class=\"ttl-en\">Recruit</span> <span class=\"ttl-jp\">リクルート</span></div><button class=\"trigger\" aria-label=\"メニューを開く\"></button>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"l-mega-nav__panel js-accordion-panel\">\n            <div>\n              <ul class=\"l-mega-nav__children\">\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit/requirement/\">募集要項</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit/requirement/#faq\">よくある質問</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/recruit/meeting/\">会社説明会のご案内</a></li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"l-mega__btn\"><a href=\"/recruit/entry/\" class=\"c-btn-circle\"><span class=\"txt u-uppercase\">Entry</span> <img class=\"arw\" src=\"/recruit/assets/images/icons/arw_circle.svg\" alt=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"18\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></div>\n  </div>\n</div>    <div class=\"l-wrapper\">\n      <div class=\"l-content\">\n        <main class=\"l-main\">\n\n<div class=\"l-page-hero\">\n  <div class=\"l-page-hero__head\">\n    <div class=\"l-inner\">\n      <h1 class=\"head-ttl\"><span class=\"ttl-en\">info session</span> <span class=\"ttl-jp\">会社説明会のご案内</span></h1>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"l-page-hero__visual\">\n    <picture>\n      <source srcset=\"/recruit/assets/images/meeting/hero_visual_sp.webp\" media=\"(max-width: 767px)\" type=\"image/webp\">\n      <source srcset=\"/recruit/assets/images/meeting/hero_visual_sp.jpg\" media=\"(max-width: 767px)\">\n      <source srcset=\"/recruit/assets/images/meeting/hero_visual.webp\" type=\"image/webp\"><img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/meeting/hero_visual.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"lazy-none\" height=\"640\" width=\"2800\">\n    </picture>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"l-breadcrumbs l-page-bread\">\n  <div class=\"l-inner\">\n    <nav>\n      <ol vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"BreadcrumbList\">\n        <li property=\"itemListElement\" typeof=\"ListItem\"><a property=\"item\" typeof=\"WebPage\" title=\"採用情報TOP\" href=\"/recruit/\"><span property=\"name\">採用情報TOP</span></a>\n          <meta property=\"position\" content=\"1\">\n        </li>\n        <li property=\"itemListElement\" typeof=\"ListItem\"><span property=\"name\">会社説明会のご案内</span>\n          <meta property=\"position\" content=\"2\">\n        </li>\n      </ol>\n    </nav>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"l-page-cont\">\n    <section class=\"l-sec-xl\">\n    <div class=\"l-inner\">\n      <div class=\"meet-ov l-sec-sm u-ta-center-lg\">\n        <h2 class=\"meet-ov__ttl\">Face to Faceによるコミュニケーションを大切にした\n          <br class=\"l-lg\">会社説明会を実施しています。\n        </h2>\n        <p class=\"meet-ov__lead\">日興商会では、皆さんが安心して第一歩を踏み出せるよう、会社説明会を開催しています。\n          <br>ビジネスモデルや、私たちが大切にしている価値観など、当社の魅力を直接感じていただける機会です。\n          <br>また、新入社員研修の一部を体験いただけるグループワークも同時開催しますので、入社後のイメージに繋げていただければと思います。\n          <br>是非、ご参加ください。\n        </p>\n      </div>\n      <nav class=\"c-pa